description:
Who is God? Is there anything about God that you don’t understand?

This #short clip from the Global Campmeeting sermon, “What Does It Mean When the Bible Calls Jesus the Son of God?” https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aObng-3kEEQ&list=PL-k2Gb-DBYo9tb9fHW_AxGxJ1R8MpNnpa&index=21 by Pastor Clinton Wahlen will remind us that God revealed to us what we need to know about Him, what we can understand and grasp, and what remains a mystery and belongs to Him. As Deuteronomy 29:29 states, “The secret things belong to the Lord our God, but those things which are revealed belong to us and to our children forever, that we may do all the words of this law. “

Watch the video to learn more about who God is as Pastor Wahlen provides a detailed explanation of who God is and who Jesus is based on Scripture.
